sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant PM as Plugin Manager
    participant Market as Marketplace
    participant Sandbox
    User->>PM: /plugin install company/workflow
    PM->>Market: 查询插件信息
    Market-->>PM: 返回 package + 签名
    PM->>PM: 验证数字签名
    PM->>User: 显示权限请求
    User->>PM: 批准
    PM->>Sandbox: 加载插件代码
    Sandbox->>Sandbox: 注册命令/钩子
    Sandbox-->>User: ✅ 插件已激活
